quran[13{c,v,t}:
19,39,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, iss haalat mein jabkay yeh log ghaafil hain aur imaan nahi laa rahay hain, aِnhin is din se dara do jabkay faisla kar diya jaye ga aur pachtaway ke siwa koi charah car nah hoga"
19,40,aakhir kaar hum hi zameen aur is ki saari cheezon ke waris hon ge aur sab hamari taraf hipalta-ay jayen ge
19,41,"aur is kitaab mein ibrahim ka qissa bayan karo, be shak woh aik raast baz ensaan aur aik nabi tha"
19,42,"( inhen zara uss mauqa ki yaad dlao ) jabkay uss ne apne baap se kaha ke"" abba jaan, aap kyun unn cheezon ki ibadat karte hain jo nah sunthee hain nah dekhatii hain aur nah aap ka koi kaam bana sakti hain ?"
19,43,"abba jaan, mere paas aik aisa ilm aaya hai jo aap ke paas nahi aaya, aap mere peechay chalein, mein aap ko seedha rasta batau ga"
19,44,"abba jaan! aap shetan ki bandagi nah karen, shetan to rehman ka nafarman hai"
19,45,"abba jaan, mujhe dar hai ke kahin aap Rehman ke azaab mein mubtala nah ho jayen aur shetan ke saathi ban kar rahen """
19,46,"baap ne kaha"" ibrahim, kya to mere mabodon se phir gaya hai? agar to baz nah aaya to mein tujhe sangsar kar dun ga bas to hamesha ke liye mujh se allag ho ja """
19,47,"ibrahim ne kaha"" salam hai aap ko mein apne rab se dua karoon ga ke aap ko maaf kar day, mera rab mujh par bara hi meharban hai"
19,48,"mein aap logon ko bhi chhorta hon aur unn hstyon ko bhi jinhein aap log khuda ko chore kar puraka karte hain mein to apne rab hi ko poukaron ga, umeed hai ke mein apne rab ko pukaar ke namuraad nah rahon ga """
19,49,pas jab woh unn logon se aur unn ke مma'bodane ghair Allah se juda ho gaya to hum ne uss ko ishaq aur yaqoob jaisi aulaad di aur har aik ko nabi banaya
19,50,aur un ko apni rehmat se nawaza aur un ko sachhi namwari ataa ki
19,51,aur zikar karo is kitaab mein moose ka woh aik cheeda shakhs tha aur rasool nabi tha
